room_title: Escape room "Trouble in Paradise" by Escape Countdown in Sarasota
room_description: While on Vacation on Siesta Key beach a freak storm rapidly approached the Sarasota Gulf Coast area!  All the weather Forecasters missed this storm of the Century! It's left you stranded on the beach with everyone else evacuated! You have to get to safety and off the island before this Category 5 Storm hits! Can you escape from the beach and Tiki Bar in time?
